{"tid":95320,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"由於產能影響，LG G6或搭載高通821芯片","createTime":"2017-01-26T02:31:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T01:00:04.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2f3b1a46887488ed2f2ca92ca5c923b1cbd2404","tid":95320,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T02:31:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.android-hk.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/%E6%9C%AA%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D-64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.android-hk.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2F%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%2591%25BD%25E5%2590%258D-64.jpg&h=1965efbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據外媒Android Police的報道，LG下一代旗艦手機G6可能無法使用高通Snapdragon 835處理器，退而求其次採用Snapdragon 821芯片。出現這一狀況的主要原因是835處理器的產能暫時無法跟上，目前各大手機廠商都在搶這款最新的頂級處理器，所以考慮到時間和產能的問題導致LG來不及發佈搭載835處理器的G6。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.android-hk.com/news/lg-g6-with-s821-android-hk-25117/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.android-hk.com%2Fnews%2Flg-g6-with-s821-android-hk-25117%2F&d=ifq9L76%2BWd08ZR2REB7OX0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=92bad92f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.android-hk.com/news/lg-g6-with-s821-android-hk-25117/</a>"},{"pid":"ffdd2450d4d857676a300de4685a93c0fa84cec8","tid":95320,"uid":79519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T02:35:17.000Z","msg":"仲未執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad3c930df2461d5d9a67ea5d23da3f98a41c9e8","tid":95320,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T02:35:21.000Z","msg":"咪又係死死氣去mk 排隊比人撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8a5952efbc7039088d8b64888e77a8ad7d74f9","tid":95320,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T02:39:41.000Z","msg":"其實我比較關心電量<br />\n如果又倒水電又無得換電<br />\n真係一件垃圾<br />\n利申： sony lg fans"},{"pid":"f20d5f39e0258d608f58026d8f2d9b9e30e739b3","tid":